title: Kevin Gates x Rustie – “Wait in Line”  (OFFICIAL VIDEO STREAM)
description:
“Wait in Line” is the fifth and final single off of the second Converse CONS compilation, CONS EP Vol. 2. Rustie recorded the music in his home recording studio in Glasgow, Scotland. Kevin Gates recorded his vocals in his mobile studio while on a perennial tour around the United States. The song was also mixed by Rustie and mastered by Grammy-nominated engineer Mike Bozzi.

Produced by: Kevin Gates x Rustie 
Music by: Rustie
Lyrics by: Kevin Gates
Vocals by: Kevin Gates
